<h1 id='balance'>Balance</h1>
<p>The Balance area on the Overview screen displays how much CHI you have in the 
<a href="wallets.md">currently selected wallet</a>.</p>

<p><img src="/images/img/balance-area.png" alt="balance-area" /></p>

<p>It displays the amount in full to 8 decimal places.</p>

<p>Should you &quot;be surprised&quot; at an amount in your wallet, it may be that you&#39;ve 
simple got the wrong one selected.</p>

<p>See <a href="wallets.md">Wallets</a> for more information.</p>
